n the vehicle log book and to the Head<\/li>\n<li>Maintain all vehicles in a clean, hygienic and tidy condition both inside and out at all times, including replacement vehicles<\/li>\n<li>Refuel vehicles as required and log all receipts<\/li>\n<li>Cover for absent colleagues<\/li>\n<li>Work within health and safety guidelines as set out in the school Minibus Drivers\u2019 Operating instructions<\/li>\n<li>To work to pre-planned schedules and complete any record of work, record of driving and accident reports that may be required by law, the School, the \u2018Code of Practice\u2019 or procedures manual<\/li>\n<li>To deal with emergencies, according to School procedure<\/li>\n<li>To be able to communicate effectively, and act as a first point of contact between children, parents, teachers and school staff<\/li>\n<li>Undertake any other associated duties as required by the Head<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4><strong>About You<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p>As this position requires you to drive the school bus, it is important you hold a Full and Clean UK Drivers Licence with D1 entitlement. We are also looking for someone who:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Has driving experience, with D1 license<\/li>\n<li>Has basic DIY skills and in-depth understanding of maintenance procedures<\/li>\n<li>Has strong problem-solving skills for addressing safety and maintenance concerns<\/li>\n<li>Is organised, good at multi-tasking and scheduling<\/li>\n<li>Ability to work occasional weekends or out of hours for events such as Open Days<\/li>\n<li><em>PCV license desirable<\/em><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>To find out more about this role, please read our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.beechwood.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/20210825-BW-Minibus-Driver-Job-Description.pdf\">Job Description<\/a><\/p>\n<h4>How To Apply<\/h4>\n<p>To apply for this role, please fill out our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.beechwood.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/20220718-BW-Application-Form.docx\">Application Form<\/a> and return this to recruitment@alphaschools.co.uk along with your CV.<\/p>\n<p><em>Beechwood School is committed to safeguarding and promoting the welfare of children. Applicants for ALL jobs will undergo appropriate child-protection screening including checks with past employers and the Disclosure and Barring Service (DBS) check to enhanced level, costs are covered by the company. This role is exempt from the Rehabilitation of Offenders Act 1974 and the Amendments to the Exceptions Order 1975, 2013 and 2020.<\/em><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Our Current Vacancies\u00a0 Minibus Driver We are looking for enthusiastic\u00a0Minibus Drivers\u00a0to join our school at\u00a0Beechwood School, in Tunbridge Wells. Beechwood School\u00a0is a&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1083,"featured_media":725,"parent":0,"menu_order":95,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v19.7.1 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Job Vacancies - Beechwood<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.beechwood.org.uk\/job-vacancies\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Job Vacancies - Beechwood\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Our Current Vacancies\u00a0 Minibus Driver We are looking for enthusiastic\u00a0Minibus Drivers\u00a0to join our school at\u00a0Beechwood School, in Tunbridge Wells. Beechwood School\u00a0is a...\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/www.beechwood.org.uk\/job-vacancies\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Beechwood\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:modified_time\" content=\"2022-09-26T08:11:20+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https:\/\/www.beechwoo